{"text_id":29950,"tokens":["In"," today","'","s"," complex"," and"," uncertain"," world",","," making"," decisions"," can"," be"," a"," daunting"," task","."," Whether"," it"," is"," deciding"," on"," a"," career"," path",","," choosing"," the"," right"," college",","," or"," making"," an"," investment",","," we"," are"," often"," faced"," with"," multiple"," options"," and"," conflicting"," information","."," In"," such"," situations",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," prove"," to"," be"," invaluable","."," This"," essay"," will"," discuss"," the"," benefits"," of"," asking"," for"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," when"," making"," a"," decision"," and"," provide"," examples"," to"," support"," the"," argument",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," key"," benefits"," of"," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," is"," gaining"," a"," broad"," perspective","."," Each"," person"," has"," their"," own"," unique"," experiences",","," biases",","," and"," knowledge",","," which"," can"," significantly"," influence"," their"," opinions"," and"," advice","."," By"," consulting"," multiple"," sources",","," we"," can"," obtain"," a"," range"," of"," viewpoints"," that"," we"," may"," not"," have"," considered"," otherwise","."," For"," instance",","," when"," deciding"," on"," a"," college"," major",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," professors",","," professionals"," in"," the"," field",","," and"," graduates"," of"," different"," programs"," can"," provide"," diverse"," insights"," and"," help"," us"," make"," a"," more"," informed"," decision",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," seeking"," advice"," from"," multiple"," sources"," can"," help"," identify"," patterns"," and"," common","alities","."," When"," various"," sources"," provide"," similar"," advice"," or"," point"," out"," the"," same"," pros"," and"," cons",","," it"," adds"," credibility"," to"," the"," information"," and"," increases"," the"," likelihood"," of"," making",